    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方Q群：983767540</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《我御剑降魔》是一款独特的修仙射击RPG，结合了修仙大世界的RPG冒险与经典卷轴飞行射击，为玩家带来全新而刺激的修仙体验。你可以实时切换小队成员，享受紧张而爽快的战斗，踏上冒险与修行并存的旅程！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/7ff3622159a3eab488a6c370422c53ae.avif?t=1747304928\" width=600 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索十二大门派、三大都城、二十五座城池和十大岛屿，每个区域都蕴藏丰富的故事与挑战，等待你的踏足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/eb2ab2cd82e44d788edb014e5c4c617c.poster.avif?t=1747304928\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/eb2ab2cd82e44d788edb014e5c4c617c.webm?t=1747304928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/eb2ab2cd82e44d788edb014e5c4c617c.mp4?t=1747304928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/58c36b4b846ffc97b1cd13c17279d8f5.avif?t=1747304928\" width=600 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供三十二种灵体与十大灵根，数百种灵根组合与先天气运，助你打造专属的修仙角色。掌握金、木、水、火、土、雷、风、冰、光、暗十系法术，修炼五百多种心法与功法，配备三百余种装备与法宝，逐步攀登修行巅峰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/694758bcbae97fd346dedaa24284f487.poster.avif?t=1747304928\" width=602 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/694758bcbae97fd346dedaa24284f487.webm?t=1747304928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/694758bcbae97fd346dedaa24284f487.mp4?t=1747304928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/c067c7d4f858fdf0393ce151280c1c4a.avif?t=1747304928\" width=600 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典的横版/纵版卷轴飞行射击玩法，从激烈的洞府攻防到刺激的PK战斗，多种模式考验你的极限操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/ebc0bc04dcc4036756608a10b4733906.poster.avif?t=1747304928\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/ebc0bc04dcc4036756608a10b4733906.webm?t=1747304928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/ebc0bc04dcc4036756608a10b4733906.mp4?t=1747304928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313440/extras/27ecd7db7902a9ded30f93044e8b1511.avif?t=1747304928\" width=600 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受多样的修仙生活，包括炼丹、炼器、阵法、符篆、种植、采集等活动，或参与拍卖、黑市交易和博彩。你的洞府可自由布置，配备灵泉、灵田、修炼室、炼丹室等，打造理想的修炼场所。</p>",
